  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will assess unstable plaque imaging features by using high resolution MR imaging
      and Sodium Fluoride F-18 PET. This is a comparative study between symptomatic and
      asymptomatic patient referred to carotid endateriectomy, with reference to pathologic
      analysis of plaque components
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
